Meeting up separately, the city breeze is a little cold.

524
00:35:10,558 --> 00:35:16,358
慣れないワイン 無理矢理飲み干してしまってはフラフラ
Gulping down wine I'm not used to, I'm already feeling dizzy.

525
00:35:16,358 --> 00:35:18,758
嫌われちゃったらどうしよう
What if you end up hating me?

526
00:35:18,758 --> 00:35:21,058
下手にしちゃったらどうしよう
What if I mess things up?

527
00:35:21,058 --> 00:35:24,558
少しも残したくない
I don't want to leave even a little bit behind.

528
00:35:26,058 --> 00:35:28,158
ちょっと期待してね
