どこか違う景色見てる
yet you're looking at some other scenery.

548
00:36:48,758 --> 00:36:51,758
いつも優しいフリして
Always pretending to be kind,

549
00:36:51,758 --> 00:36:54,558
そんなんじゃないのに笑って
smiling even though you're not like that.

550
00:36:54,558 --> 00:36:59,558
近づけば近づくほど心は遠くなって
The closer we get, the further apart our hearts become.

551
00:36:59,558 --> 00:37:03,558
少しずつ離れていくことは分かるよ
I know we're slowly drifting apart.

552
00:37:03,558 --> 00:37:08,558
今夜は忘れるほど抱きしめて
Tonight, hug me tight enough to forget everything.

553
