取り繕った私は流れていく
My made-up self is washing away.

564
00:38:01,558 --> 00:38:06,558
今夜は忘れるほど抱きしめて
Tonight, hug me tight enough to forget everything.

565
00:39:11,558 --> 00:39:15,558
chocolate box

566
