604
00:40:40,339 --> 00:40:43,839
君の一生懸命さに ついつい忘れちゃう
I end up forgetting your earnestness...

605
00:40:43,839 --> 00:40:46,839
誰よりも一番 大好きなのに
...even though I love you more than anyone.

606
00:40:46,839 --> 00:40:49,839
甘い甘い夢の宝箱
Sweet, sweet, dream's treasure box...

607
00:40:49,839 --> 00:40:53,339
奇跡味の秘密のチョコレート
...miracle-flavored secret chocolate.

608
