00:49:57,653 --> 00:50:00,653
体温計...
I wonder if my thermometer...

699
00:50:01,506 --> 00:50:05,006
…ちゃったかな？
...I wonder?

700
00:50:07,006 --> 00:50:11,006
自分のことわからないまま
Though I still don't know myself very well,

701
00:50:11,006 --> 00:50:15,006
あの子にアドバイスまでしちゃって
I even gave her advice,

702
00:50:15,006 --> 00:50:19,506
胸が痛いや
and it made my chest hurt.

703
00:50:20,006 --> 00:50:27,006
世界は恋に落ちている 光の矢胸を射す
The whole world is falling in love, an arrow of light striking our chests.

704
00:50:27,006 --> 00:50:35,006
気づいたこの想いは 「もう、遅いの」
I've just realized these feelings, "is it too late?"

705
00:50:35,006 --> 00:50:42,506
あの子のほうが可愛いのに知ってるよだけど
I know that she's cuter than I am, but...

706
00:50:42,506 --> 00:50:49,506
「うまくいかないで」なんてね 逃げ出したくせに
"I hope it doesn't work out," I thought, even though I'm the one who ran away.

707
00:50:49,506 --> 00:50:55,006
ちょこ、君のこと全部わかりたいって思っちゃった。これが恋だって、初めて気づいたの。
Choco, I found myself wanting to know everything about you. I finally realized that this is love.

708
00:50:55,006 --> 00:50:59,006
絶対振り向いてほしい。遅かったけど、諦めたくない。
I definitely want you to look my way. Even if it's late, I don't want to give up.

709
00:50:59,006 --> 00:51:02,506
だって、好きだから！
Because, I love you!

710
00:51:02,506 --> 00:51:07,006
春に咲いた
The flower that bloomed...

711
00:51:07,006 --> 00:51:10,006
花が恋をした
...in spring fell in love.

712
00:51:10,006 --> 00:51:14,006
花は
The flower...

713
00:51:14,006 --> 00:51:17,006
必死に上を向いて笑った
...desperately looked upward and smiled.

714
00:51:17,006 --> 00:51:21,006
青い夏の
A bud...

715
00:51:21,006 --> 00:51:24,506
蕾も恋をした
...in the blue summer also fell in love.

716
00:51:24,506 --> 00:51:29,006
咲かない花と
An unopened flower...

717
00:51:29,006 --> 00:51:31,506
火薬の匂い
...and the scent of gunpowder.

718
00:51:47,006 --> 00:51:50,506
本当の気持ち 言葉にして
I want to express my true feelings,

719
00:51:50,506 --> 00:51:54,506
大事なこと 話せたら<
if I can say what is important...

720
00:51:54,506 --> 00:52:01,506
今日もリスタート
...I'll restart today again.

721
00:52:01,506 --> 00:52:05,506
鈍感な君だから
You're dense,

722
00:52:05,506 --> 00:52:09,006
口に出していわなきゃ
so I have to say it out loud.

723
00:52:09,006 --> 00:52:13,006
今君に伝えるよ
I'll tell you now,

724
00:52:13,006 --> 00:52:17,006
「ねえ、好きです」
"hey, I love you."

725
00:52:17,006 --> 00:52:23,506
世界は恋に落ちている 光の矢胸を射す
The whole world is falling in love, an arrow of light striking our chests.

726
00:52:23,506 --> 00:52:31,506
全部わかりたいんだよ 「ねえ、聞かせて」
I want to understand everything, "hey, let me know."

727
00:52:31,506 --> 00:52:38,506
たぐりよせて もうゼロセンチ
Pulling you close, to zero-centimeters...

728
00:52:38,506 --> 00:52:45,506
駆け抜けた日々に
...in the days passing by.

729
00:52:45,506 --> 00:52:52,506
忘れない 忘れない 輝く一ページ
I won't forget, I can't forget this one, shining page.

730
00:53:22,006 --> 00:53:24,506
はい！ということで
Alright! And with that,

731
00:53:24,506 --> 00:53:29,506
ここまではアキさま、ロボ子、
up until here, with Aki-sama, Roboco,

732
00:53:29,506 --> 00:53:33,006
ござるに...
and Gozaru...

733
00:53:33,006 --> 00:53:38,006
歌、一緒に歌わせていただきました！
we sang songs together!

734
00:53:38,006 --> 00:53:42,006
みんなありがとう！
Thank you everyone!

735
00:53:42,006 --> 00:53:45,506
さてさて、ここからは
Well then, from here on,

736
00:53:45,506 --> 00:53:50,506
なんと！重大告知が２つあります！
there are actually two major announcements!

737
00:53:50,506 --> 00:53:54,006
まず１つ目が...
First, the first one is...

738
00:53:54,006 --> 00:53:57,006
こちら！ドドン！
This! Ba-bam!

739
00:53:57,006 --> 00:54:03,506
癒月ちょこ誕生日記念2026！
Yuzuki Choco Birthday Celebration 2026!

740
00:54:03,506 --> 00:54:07,506
それではちょっと詳しくご紹介していきたいと思います。
Now, I'd like to introduce it in a bit more detail.

741
00:54:07,506 --> 00:54:10,006
まずは、こちら！
First, this one!

742
00:54:10,006 --> 00:54:15,006
ちょこのクッション！
Choco's Cushion!

743
00:54:15,006 --> 00:54:20,006
いやこれね、ちょこの誕生日といえば...
You know, speaking of Choco's birthday...

744
00:54:20,006 --> 00:54:23,506
毎年、Nardack先生ありがとうございますということで！
Every year, I say thank you to Nardack-sensei!

745
00:54:23,506 --> 00:54:28,006
今年もNardack先生に...
This year as well, Nardack-sensei...

746
00:54:28,006 --> 00:54:33,006
めちゃめちゃ素敵なイラスト描き下ろしていただきました！
drew this super lovely illustration for me!

747
00:54:33,006 --> 00:54:37,006
今回のテーマはバレンタインということで！
With this year's theme being Valentine's!

748
00:54:37,006 --> 00:54:42,006
ちょっとね、チョコメイトを抱きながら...
Holding the Chocolat Mate...

749
00:54:42,006 --> 00:54:46,506
ちょっと今回はチョコレート型のクッションにしてみました！
I made it into a chocolate-shaped cushion this time!

750
00:54:46,506 --> 00:54:49,506
可愛いでしょ？
Isn't it cute?

751
00:54:49,506 --> 00:54:54,006
サイズ感がちょうど枕くらいになってるので
The size is just about like a pillow,

752
00:54:54,006 --> 00:54:58,506
ちょっとねお昼寝のときとか、仮眠用に「すやぁ」ってできる
so you can use it for a quick nap, sleeping soundly with it,

753
00:54:58,506 --> 00:55:01,506
感じで使えちゃいます！
like that!

754
00:55:01,506 --> 00:55:04,506
そして、続いてはこちら！
And next is this one!

755
00:55:05,726 --> 00:55:06,726
なんと！
Guess what!

756
00:55:06,726 --> 00:55:08,026
今回
This time...

757
00:55:08,026 --> 00:55:09,926
初めてちょっとね
...for the very first time,

758
00:55:09,926 --> 00:55:10,126
お菓子が...
you can make sweets...

759
01:00:05,542 --> 01:00:06,842
わー！
Wow!

760
01:00:06,842 --> 01:00:08,542
しかもこちら！
What's more, here...

761
01:00:08,542 --> 01:00:14,842
なんと、オリ曲に、ストーリー連動のボイスドラマが、
Incredibly, a story-linked voice drama...

762
01:00:14,842 --> 01:00:18,542
一緒に、リリースされます！
...will be released together with the original songs!

763
01:00:19,542 --> 01:00:21,542
いや、こちらね。
Well, you see,

764
01:00:21,542 --> 01:00:24,342
約1話から12話まで！
from episode 1 to 12!

765
01:00:24,342 --> 01:00:26,842
1曲ずつに連動して、
Linked to each individual song,

766
01:00:26,842 --> 01:00:30,042
ボイスドラマもあるので、
there will also be a voice drama,

767
01:00:30,042 --> 01:00:33,542
ぜひぜひ楽しみにしといてください！
so please look forward to them!

768
01:00:34,042 --> 01:00:36,342
そして、今回はね。
And this time,

769
01:00:36,342 --> 01:00:38,542
その記念すべき...
we will celebrate...

770
01:00:38,542 --> 01:00:40,342
1曲目を、
the very first song...

771
01:00:40,342 --> 01:00:44,542
これから披露したいと思います！
...by performing it right now!

772
01:00:45,042 --> 01:00:47,042
それでは聴いてください。
Please listen to...

773
01:00:47,042 --> 01:00:49,542
『キミの秒針』
"Your Second Hand."

774
01:01:00,842 --> 01:01:05,342
まだ戻れないから
Because I can't go back yet,

775
01:01:05,342 --> 01:01:08,542
また...
once more...

776
01:01:08,542 --> 01:01:12,342
愛しさが増す
my affection grows.

777
01:01:12,342 --> 01:01:17,342
キミに...
To you...

778
01:01:17,342 --> 01:01:22,542
会いたいよ
I want to see you.

779
01:01:33,542 --> 01:01:36,742
キミから受け取った
The fragile story

780
01:01:36,742 --> 01:01:39,342
壊れそうなストーリー
I received from you...

781
01:01:39,342 --> 01:01:42,042
どこまでも広がる
spread endlessly across...

782
01:01:42,042 --> 01:01:44,542
青い青い空
...the blue, blue sky.

783
01:01:44,542 --> 01:01:47,042
変わらない毎日も
The unchanging everyday life,

784
01:01:47,042 --> 01:01:49,542
色のない夢も
and the colorless dreams...

785
01:01:49,542 --> 01:01:54,542
手放して はじめようよ
Let's let go and begin.

786
01:01:54,542 --> 01:01:59,542
不安の夜を数え
Counting the nights of anxiety,

787
01:01:59,542 --> 01:02:05,542
泣きながら迎えた朝でもいい
even if we greet the morning in tears, it's fine.

788
01:02:07,542 --> 01:02:13,042
時計の針のように
Like the hands of a clock,

789
01:02:13,042 --> 01:02:18,742
刻んだ思い出たち広がった
the engraved memories spread out.

790
01:02:18,742 --> 01:02:23,042
戻れないから また
Because I can't go back, once more

791
01:02:23,042 --> 01:02:26,542
愛しさが増す
my affection grows.

792
01:02:26,542 --> 01:02:31,542
キミに会いたいよ
I want to see you.

793
01:02:40,042 --> 01:02:42,842
二人で暖めた
The precious story

794
01:02:42,842 --> 01:02:45,542
大切なストーリー...
we warmed together...

795
01:02:45,542 --> 01:02:48,042
遠くまで続いた
The endless path

796
01:02:48,042 --> 01:02:50,542
果てない道
that continued so far.

797
01:02:50,542 --> 01:02:53,542
「疲れたら代わるから」
"I'll take over if you get tired,"

798
01:02:53,542 --> 01:02:56,542
そう言ってくれた
is what you told me.

799
01:02:56,542 --> 01:03:01,542
優しさに触れて見えた
Feeling your kindness, I could see...

800
01:03:01,542 --> 01:03:06,542
受け入れてくれたこと
...the things you accepted for me.

801
01:03:06,542 --> 01:03:12,542
忘れない 嬉しくて満ちた日
I won't forget those happy, fulfilling days.

802
01:03:14,542 --> 01:03:20,042
雨上がりの胸に
In my heart after the rain,

803
01:03:20,042 --> 01:03:25,542
かかった虹のように綺麗な
beautiful like a rainbow...

804
01:03:25,542 --> 01:03:30,542
キミからの言葉
The words from you...

805
01:03:30,542 --> 01:03:35,542
一つ一つが今も宝物
each and every one is still a treasure to me.

806
01:03:46,742 --> 01:03:51,542
支えてくれたから
Because you supported me,

807
01:03:51,542 --> 01:03:57,542
輝けるこの気持ち届けよう
I will deliver these shining feelings to you.

808
01:03:59,542 --> 01:04:05,042
時計の針のように
Like the hands of a clock,

809
01:04:05,042 --> 01:04:10,542
刻んだ思い出たち広がった
the engraved memories spread out.

810
01:04:10,542 --> 01:04:15,542
戻れないから また
Because I can't go back, once more

811
01:04:15,542 --> 01:04:18,542
愛しさが増す
my affection grows.

812
01:04:18,542 --> 01:04:21,542
キミに会いたいよ
I want to see you.

813
01:04:21,542 --> 01:04:26,542
雨上がりの胸に
In my heart after the rain,

814
01:04:26,542 --> 01:04:32,042
かかった虹のように綺麗な
beautiful like a rainbow...

815
01:04:32,042 --> 01:04:36,542
キミからの言葉
The words from you...

816
01:04:36,542 --> 01:04:44,542
一つ一つが今も宝物
each and every one is still a treasure to me.

817
01:05:11,298 --> 01:05:15,198
はい！ということで、みんなどうだったかな？
Yes! So, everyone, how was it?

818
01:05:15,298 --> 01:05:18,498
今回の新曲「キミの秒針」は、
This time's new song, "Kimi no Byoushin,"

819
01:05:18,598 --> 01:05:22,298
シドのマオ様が作詞、
had its lyrics written by Mao-sama of SID,

820
01:05:22,398 --> 01:05:27,098
そして御恵明希様が作曲、編曲、
and music composed and arranged by Aki-sama of SID.

821
01:05:27,198 --> 01:05:33,098
そして編曲にはなんと、加藤貴之様も加わっていただきました！
And for the arrangement, Takayuki Kato-sama also joined us!

822
01:05:33,298 --> 01:05:36,298
いや、今回は、
Wow, this time,

823
01:05:36,398 --> 01:05:40,298
ボイスドラマ連動企画の第1弾として、
as the first part of the voice drama collaboration project,

824
01:05:40,398 --> 01:05:48,298
ストーリー全体のね、テーマソングを担うような、ハイクオリティの楽曲に仕上がっております！
it has turned out to be a high-quality song that serves as the theme song for the entire story!

825
01:05:49,298 --> 01:05:57,298
ま、ドラマの鍵となるね、「秒針」というメタファーにも要注目してください！
Please also pay attention to the metaphor of the "second hand," which is key to the drama!

826
01:05:57,798 --> 01:06:07,798
シドさんだけではなく、この後のね、豪華アーティストの皆様にもたくさん書いていただいたので、
Not only SID, but many other gorgeous artists have also written songs for us after this,

827
01:06:07,898 --> 01:06:12,798
皆様、リリースをお楽しみに！
so please look forward to the releases!

828
01:06:13,298 --> 01:06:19,498
こちらの「キミの秒針」は、各音楽サイトはちょっと間が空いちゃうんだけど、
As for "Kimi no Byoushin," although there will be a bit of a gap on music streaming sites,

829
01:06:19,798 --> 01:06:25,298
3月15日の0時から配信予定でございます！
it is scheduled to be distributed starting from midnight on March 15th!

830
01:06:25,798 --> 01:06:36,298
ま、ちょっとね、公開まで時間があるから、それまでこの配信、何度も見返してみてください！聴き込んでね！
Well, since there's some time until the release, please watch this stream over and over! Listen to it a lot!

831
01:06:37,298 --> 01:06:47,298
そして、 Marshallー、MVもね、ちょっと後日公開なので、楽しみにしていてください！
And, and! The MV will also be released at a later date, so please look forward to it!

832
01:06:48,798 --> 01:06:57,298
ということで、今日のチョコの生誕ライブはどうだったかな？
And with that, how was Choco's birthday live today?

833
01:06:58,298 --> 01:07:03,298
ま、この後はすぐに、
Well, right after this,

834
01:07:03,398 --> 01:07:18,498
ちょっとね、冒頭、最初の方でお披露目した、ノエルちゃんとラミィちゃんとの3人の「初恋大戦争」のMV公開があって、
we'll have the release of the MV for "Hatsukoi Daisensou" by the three of us with Noel-chan and Lamy-chan, which we showed at the beginning,

835
01:07:18,798 --> 01:07:27,298
その後、メン限で、ちょっとライブと、撮影会の続きとか、
and after that, in the members-only stream, we'll do a mini-live, continue the photo session,Convert the provided video translation files into high-quality, audio-synchronized English subtitles using your advanced multimodal capabilities. Ensure exact alignment between spoken dialogue and subtitle timestamps.

836
01:07:27,398 --> 01:07:36,298
ちょっとね、メン限でしか見れないシチュエーションドラマとかやるので、
and do a situation drama that you can only see in the members-only stream!

837
01:07:36,398 --> 01:07:42,298
ぜひぜひ、気になる人は見に来てください！
So please, those who are interested, come and watch!

838
01:07:43,298 --> 01:07:46,298
それでは、また後でお会いしましょう！
Well then, let's meet again later!

839
01:07:47,298 --> 01:07:56,298
お疲れーと！はーむっ。
Otsukare-to! *chu*

